It's 99% certain that CIA field operatives use one-time pads or something
equivalent to generate a one-time-pad data stream.

There's a bit of a write-up of this in Big Secrets, along with suggestions
of where the tansmitter stations are.  (Mainland US, not Cuba etc etc as
often suggested)

